<p><strong>The Problem:</strong> Domestic violence is underreported for many reasons; a major reason being that victims often feel alone and are made to believe (by their abusers) that they are not cared for, and nobody will help them if they report their abuse. Victims of abuse looking to leave those situations will only do so if they have support. We decided to reimagine the website of this shelter by making centering support to encourage victims to make the transition to survivors.</p>

<div class="gallery-box">
  <div class="gallery">
    <img src="/images/rw/4_Web_Home-7.png" alt="Redwood" />
    <img src="/images/rw/5_Web_Homeâ€“8.png" alt="Redwood" />
