<p><strong>Research:</strong> Studying The Problem
Because this was a redesign, the first cause of action was conducting a heuristic analysis on the current website. Hereâ€™s what we discovered:</p>
<ul>
  <li>website had lots of navigation issues (broken links, no breadcrumbs).</li>
  <li>information was difficult to find (no search bar).</li>
  <li>no uniformity in colour or font style.</li>
</ul>

<div class="gallery-box">
  <div class="gallery">
    <img src="/images/rw/6_Web_Homeâ€“12.png" alt="Redwood" />
    <img src="/images/rw/7_Web_Homeâ€“13.png" alt="Redwood" />
